<HL>
   Who's News:
   Sequa Corp.
</HL>
<DATE>
04/27/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   SQAA WNEWS
</CO>
<LP>
   SEQUA Corp. (New York) -- Antonio L. Savoca, president of
the Atlantic Research Corp. subsidiary; Daniel L. Marquitz,
president of the Valley Line unit; and John Cabrey, vice
president of the Sequa Chemicals unit, were elected vice
presidents of this company, which makes and repairs jet
engines, and has interests in military electronics and
electro-optics, marine transportation, and machinery used to
make food and beverage cans.
</LP>
<TEXT>
